parameters.message: That was a refreshing shower.
Let's go to my first day of class!

I look for my designated cooking island. Looking around the class, I see Keisuke, Rokuko and Orika. They are all focused.
The fact that Rokuko is focused is weird, since she said yesterday that she was here only for a degree.
But I won't let that take place on my mind. The class will start, I should focus as well.
